results.description:
White Rock lake, sunset bay
I gots a fish & you don't!
Photo 1:  Flaunting The Catch
Most birds swallow their fish immediately.  This egret decided to stroll past the pelican as though flaunting its prize.
Photo 2:  Walking Past The Pelican
It was a tiny shad, just a nibble really.  Not sure why the egret decided to walk around with it for awhile. 
Photo 3:  Pelican Could Not Care Less
The pelican did not show the slightest interest in the egret's fish.
